title: Seadive Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Filipino, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of the Seadive Resort and Dive Centre. With limited veg options in this remote town, serves a vegan vegetable curry, fruit platter (with no bread) and other vegan dishes or ones that can be made vegan. Wi-fi. Relaxing atmosphere, with a view, with open air seating and warm sea breezes.
